{"tid":2211100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白俄再有10萬人示威，黑客公開2千警員個人資料","createTime":"2020-09-21T02:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T03:10:10.000Z","uid":30040,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2342d30e7e74c79376b4f4c84e0c281c431fbb02","tid":2211100,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:08:55.000Z","msg":"白俄羅斯首都明斯克的大規模示威持續，星期日再有超過10萬人上街，要求總統盧卡申科下台。有示威者向防暴警察投擲玻璃，亦有示威者拉下警員的面罩，多人被帶走，有警員一度向天開槍示警。人權組織指警方至少拘捕196人。 有黑客公開2000名警員的個人資料，以示不滿警方拘捕數以千名示威者，質疑是濫捕以及有毆打被捕人士的情況。一個報道反對派消息的Telegram刊出聲明，指只要當局持續拘捕示威者，便會繼續公布更多警員資料。政府否認有虐待被拘留人士，強調會調查事件並追究責任。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2358101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2358101&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZohnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=baa28d04\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2358101</a>"},{"pid":"2384a35f72319b423f24f93238fc9c5f5fa59d22","tid":2211100,"uid":249794,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"上下街就諗住政府會改變?<br />\n唔識出刀有咩用?<br />\n得10萬人其他人對唔對得住義士?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講完都覺得平時d放負撚on9"},{"pid":"ded8ea165814d9567b87e1645b705d9a25091af3","tid":2211100,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca5e21db254139822f2e3ae239011b4e7f154ca","tid":2211100,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed42e3ddb7f6ceab5a6156d51bf68ab7ddd7c39c","tid":2211100,"uid":3241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:15:39.000Z","msg":"棒打不孝狗係全球標準黎"},{"pid":"563ef19999b02c6b86d1089adfbf26980064195f","tid":2211100,"uid":366245,"like":